Account: A HOL entity created for any addresses which interact with
Superfluid contracts.

types.description:
AccountTokenSnapshot: An aggregate entity which aggregates data on an account's
interaction with a `token`.

fields.description: ID composed of: accountID-tokenID
fields.name: id

fields.description: The number of currently open streams.
fields.name: totalNumberOfActiveStreams

fields.description: The number of all-time closed streams.
fields.name: totalNumberOfClosedStreams

fields.description: The current (as of updatedAt) number of subscriptions with units allocated to them tied to this `account`.

fields.description: Counts all currently (as of updatedAt) approved subscriptions whether or not they have units.
fields.name: totalApprovedSubscriptions

fields.description: Balance of `account` as of `updatedAtTimestamp`/`updatedAtBlock`.
fields.name: balanceUntilUpdatedAt

fields.description: The total net flow rate of the `account` as of `updatedAtTimestamp`/`updatedAtBlock`.

fields.description: The total inflow rate (receive flowRate per second) of the `account`.

fields.description: The total outflow rate (send flowrate per second) of the `account`.

fields.description:
The total amount of `token` streamed to this `account` until
the `updatedAtTimestamp`/`updatedAtBlock`.
fields.name: totalAmountStreamedUntilUpdatedAt

fields.description: The total amount of `token` this `account` has transferred.
fields.name: totalAmountTransferredUntilUpdatedAt

FlowUpdated: An `Event` entity that is emitted

0 = create

fields.description: The number of subscriptions which have units allocated to them on the `Index`.

The number of units allocated by the `Index` that are pending.
This refers to the current (as of updatedAt) `totalUnitsPending`
- not all that has ever been pending.

This refers to the current (as of updatedAt) `totalUnitsApproved`
- not all that has ever been approved.

fields.name: totalUnits

fields.description: The total amount distributed from this `Index`.
fields.name: totalAmountDistributedUntilUpdatedAt

The subscriptions of the index, it will include approved, unapproved
and deleted subscriptions.

types.description:
IndexSubscription: A HOL entity that contains subscription data for a `subscriber` account of a particular
`Index`.

fields.description: ID composed of: subscriberAddress-publisherAddress-tokenAddress-IndexId
fields.name: id

fields.description:
Approved subscriptions don't require subscribers to claim tokens that are distributed from
the publisher.
fields.name: approved

fields.description:
If units is 0, it indicates that the subscription is "deleted". They are no longer
subscribed to the index.
fields.name: units

fields.description:
The total amount of tokens you've received via IDA until
`updatedAtTimestamp`/`updatedAtBlock`.
fields.name: totalAmountReceivedUntilUpdatedAt

fields.description:
The previous index value - used to calculate `totalAmountReceivedUntilUpdatedAt` field as of the
`index.updatedAtTimestamp`. The formula to get this value is:
`IndexSubscription.totalAmountReceivedUntilUpdatedAt + ((index.newIndexValue - indexSubscription.indexValueUntilUpdatedAt) * indexSubscription.units)`.
fields.name: indexValueUntilUpdatedAt

fields.description: IndexSubscription approved events on the subscription.
fields.name: subscriptionApprovedEvents

considered "dead". The next stream you create with the same `sender` and `receiver`

between the same `sender` and `receiver`.
